## Documents (PDF)

- ✅ `DocumentService` — tenant-branded PDF generation (DomPDF)
  - Broker identity: PlatformTenant DBA/logo/colour → org profile → shipper profile
  - Carrier identity: CarrierProfile (MC#, DOT#, address)
- ✅ Shared Blade layout — coloured header with logo or brand name, footer with legal line
- ✅ **Rate Confirmation** — per FreightJob
  - Parties, load details, stop table, rate breakdown, standard terms, signature lines
  - `GET /api/v1/jobs/{job}/rate-confirmation`
  - Frontend button on job detail header (posted / in_progress / completed)
- ✅ **Carrier Agreement** — per Contract
  - Standing rate agreement, all rate fields, 7 standard legal clauses, signature block
  - `GET /api/v1/contracts/{contract}/agreement`
  - Frontend button in ContractDrawer
- ✅ **Bill of Lading (BOL)** — travels with freight, per FreightJob at dispatch
  - Tenant-branded, stops table, commodity/weight, shipper + carrier details
  - `GET /api/v1/jobs/{job}/bol`
  - Stored to `documents` disk (S3/R2 in prod, public disk in dev); key + URL saved to `freight_jobs`
  - Frontend button in job header (posted / in_progress / completed)
- ✅ **Proof of Delivery (POD)** — two types: Proof of Pickup + Proof of Delivery, per stop
  - Photo evidence: carrier uploads photos at each stop (JPEG/PNG/HEIC/WebP, up to 50MB)
  - Signature capture: digital signature pad (HTML canvas, touch/mouse), saves base64 PNG to storage
  - PDF embeds all stop photos + drawn signature; tenant-branded
  - `GET/POST /api/v1/jobs/{job}/stops/{stop}/evidence` — upload/list photos
  - `POST /api/v1/jobs/{job}/stops/{stop}/signature` — capture signature
  - `GET/POST /api/v1/jobs/{job}/stops/{stop}/pod` — view/generate POD PDF
  - Stored persistently on `documents` disk; key + URL saved to `job_stops`
  - Frontend: camera button + photo gallery on each stop card; Generate POD / View POD button
- ✅ **Invoice / Settlement Statement** — shipper-facing payment doc
  - Auto-numbered (`INV-YYYY-XXXXXX`), tenant-branded PDF
  - Line items from `cost_breakdown` (freight, fuel surcharge, platform fee)
  - Bill-to shipper org details, bill-from broker/platform details
  - Payment status badge (Paid / Processing / Unpaid)
  - Remittance instructions if unpaid; net-30 default payment terms
  - `GET /api/v1/jobs/{job}/invoice`
  - Stored on `documents` disk; key + URL saved to `freight_jobs`
  - Frontend: Invoice button in doc header row + View Invoice link in billing panel

